          "username": "tomas.ruiz_OBIC",
          "name": "Tomas Ruiz QM",
          "createdAt": "2026-07-08T19:15:31Z",
          "text": "**Failure Pattern**\n**Task Design Trigger**\n**A  Breaks Functionality**\nDesign the optimization so the mechanical transformation has a common pitfall (lazy-loading with child route modules that redefine path segments; React.memo on a component whose props include callbacks). Include at least one previously-passing E2E route test.\n**B  Wrong Layer**\nHave the target function called from 3+ independent callers across different modules. Make one caller not go through the obvious 'service' abstraction. Require the optimization to benefit all callers.\n**C  Harness Mismatch**\nState the harness format in the first sentence of the prompt ('deliverable must be loadable by require() in plain Node  no TypeScript, no Jest'). Put the test harness file in the repository so the model can read it.\n**D  Goal Not Met**\nSpecify a numeric performance target (bundle size under X kB, response time under Y ms). Require the model to report before-and-after measurements.",
